Generate TSO Report

Source: R/rmd.R
tso_rmd.Rd

Generates a HTML report with results from the UMCCR TSO500 ctDNA workflow.

tso_rmd(tidy_rds, out_dir, prefix, quiet = FALSE)

Arguments

tidy_rds

Path to RDS object output from tso_tidy.

out_dir

Output directory.

prefix

Prefix of output file(s).

quiet

Suppress warning and other messages.

Value

Path to rendered HTML report.

Examples

if (FALSE) {
tidy_rds <- "~/tmp/tso/SBJ02858.rds"
tso_tidy(...) |> saveRDS(tidy_rds)
quiet <- TRUE
out_dir <- file.path("~/tmp/tso/out2")
prefix <- "SBJ02858"
tso_rmd(tidy_rds = tidy_rds, out_dir = out_dir, prefix = prefix, quiet = quiet)
}
